These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: fanta, soy-milk
2 different pets are kept: rabbit, ferret
There are 2 different nationalities: italian, mexican
House: palace, wooden
1. the owner of the ferret is on the left or right of the person drinking fanta##3
2. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the owner of the ferret##1
3. the wooden house is on the right of the italian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2     |
| Beverage      | soy-milk      | fanta    |
| Pet           | ferret | rabbit |
| Nationality   | italian       | mexican  |
| House     | palace      | wooden     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-2::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: fantasy, spy
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: punk, r&b
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: daisy, iris
The people use 2 different means of transport: airplane, scooter
1. the person who growsdaisy is on the left or right of the person driving the scooter##3
2. the person watching spy movies is on the left of the fan of r&b##1
3. the person driving the scooter is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |
| Movie-Genre          | spy | fantasy |
| Music-Genre   | punk       | r&b         |
| Flower           | iris     | daisy         |
| Transport     | scooter    | airplane    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-3::.
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: june, march
2 different pets are kept: pony, ferret
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: folk, r&b
The people use 2 different means of transport: quad-bike, scooter
1. the fan of r&b is on the far right##1
2. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left of the owner of the pony##1
3. the person driving the scooter is on the left or right of the person driving the quad-bike##3
4. the person driving the scooter is on the left of the fan of r&b##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |        1        |      2      |
| Birthday         | march          | june |
| Pet           | ferret | pony     |
| Music-Genre   | folk            | r&b         |
| Transport     | scooter         | quad-bike   |

