.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-4::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: cola, tea
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: action, epic
The people have 2 different hobbies: card-games, filmmaking
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: biathlon, basketball
1. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left or right of the person who's sport is basketball##3
2. the person drinking tea is the person who's sport is biathlon##1
3. the person drinking cola is on the right of the person watching epic movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |
| Beverage      | tea     | cola   |
| Movie-Genre   | epic    | action |
| Hobby   | card-games   | filmmaking |
| Sport           | biathlon | basketball    |

