.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-20::.
City: paris, hannover
There 2 different types of food: eggplant, papaya
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: folk, jazz
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: begonia, marigold
1. the fan of jazz is on the left of the person traveling to paris##1
2. the person eating eggplant is the fan of folk##1
3. the fan of folk is the person who growsmarigold##1
4. the person who growsbegonia is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |
| City      | hannover     | paris |
| Food          | papaya   | eggplant |
| Music-Genre   | jazz     | folk     |
| Flower     | begonia | marigold     |

 